{"tid":1723812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住70歲伯伯我要消費你","createTime":"2019-11-15T09:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T10:31:44.000Z","uid":232565,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd1e2a9396f8f9d699dca4f05f9c90d1b51ad14","tid":1723812,"uid":232565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:40:58.000Z","msg":"啱唔番到屋企諗住沖個涼換件衫咁啱撞正我屋企嘅深藍老豆番黎，之後佢開咗部電視睇新聞。見到70歲呀伯果單嘢。佢話：<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「蒙哂面點拉呀！」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢句嘢我有兩個解讀：<br />\n<br />\n解讀1: 班死暴徒殺完人唔洗負責任啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解讀2: <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">班警甴實啦唔到人啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第2個解讀代表咩？代表警甴無能，蒙面法又廢，政府都做過嘅嘢唔單止廢，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係好撚廢呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係時候將個波dum番畀政府<br />\n我地嘅態度要係：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係呀我地手足係錯手，但係我地都真係深表遺憾，不過你拉到人咪拉囉，叻哥話依加科技好先進，蒙面都拉到㗎嘛。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n上之中聯辦塗鴉國徽果單嘢冇記錯班曱甴用咗半個禮拜，希望手足走得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後想同班偽黃講</span><br />\n做錯咪認囉，認咗咪改囉<br />\n講撚都明核爆都唔割就核爆都唔割啦<br />\n如果呢單嘢出咗黎之後你要諗藉口開脫自己，咁你要諗下你係咪偽黃啦<br />\n<br />\n手足如果你未走嘅話你可以自首（你唔撚係condom呀，你謀殺分分鐘判終身㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n但係我求下你，你走啦好唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋70歲伯伯對唔住我要消費你"},{"pid":"4cd304927593b2f09dd086f4fe966d00ca0a2c7c","tid":1723812,"uid":232565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:44:57.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"2d876a0c75efee0f0e0a238cd1a2137f4539de8b","tid":1723812,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":